{"tid":1176363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立場報道 【逃犯條例】林鄭拒絕公開辯論 涂謹申：不將香港市民放在眼內","createTime":"2019-05-29T07:28:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T04:52:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"fb9d77f704e2e14030c9ba27861cd02b1c22c984","tid":1176363,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T07:28:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%8B%92%E7%B5%95%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E8%BE%AF%E8%AB%96-%E6%B6%82%E8%AC%B9%E7%94%B3-%E4%B8%8D%E5%B0%87%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E6%94%BE%E5%9C%A8%E7%9C%BC%E5%85%A7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%258B%2592%25E7%25B5%2595%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2596%258B%25E8%25BE%25AF%25E8%25AB%2596-%25E6%25B6%2582%25E8%25AC%25B9%25E7%2594%25B3-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25B0%2587%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2594%25BE%25E5%259C%25A8%25E7%259C%25BC%25E5%2585%25A7%2F&d=DJJewhOFhIMK5JRdM%2BI1LmINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=fbbb2be8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E6%258B%2592%25E7%25B5%2595%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%2596%258B%25E8%25BE%25AF%25E8%25AB%2596-%25E6%25B6%2582%25E8%25AC%25B9%25E7%2594%25B3-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25B0%2587%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2594%25BE%25E5%259C%25A8%25E7%259C%25BC%25E5%2585%25A7%2F&h=00a0db75\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%8B%92%E7%B5%95%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E8%BE%AF%E8%AB%96-%E6%B6%82%E8%AC%B9%E7%94%B3-%E4%B8%8D%E5%B0%87%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E6%94%BE%E5%9C%A8%E7%9C%BC%E5%85%A7/</a><br />\n<br />\n立場報道<br />\n【逃犯條例】林鄭拒絕公開辯論 涂謹申：不將香港市民放在眼內<br />\n2019/5/27 &mdash; 20:30<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/777-11_QG0sN_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F777-11_QG0sN_1200x0.png&h=ad342dfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府強推《逃犯條例》，25 名民主派議員今早邀請特首林鄭月娥，和民主黨涂謹申公開電視辯論，特首辦下午拒絕，指立法會是務實討論修例最合適的場所。涂謹申對特首的回應感到失望和遺憾，認為她放棄向市民解釋修例的機會，「反映她根本不打算聆聽港人意見，不將香港市民的利益放在眼內」。<br />\n<br />\n涂謹申表示，電視辯論可以向全港市民解釋修例正反理據，過程公開、公平、公正，既然政府一直指市民反對修例是因為不了解修例內容，林鄭月娥更應該出席辯論直接向市民解釋，而不是選擇性和個別團體閉門推銷。他又指出，即使市民真的不了解修例內容，也是政府一手造成，因為政府只就修例諮詢 20 日，公開辯論可以讓市民看清正反理據再自行判斷是否支持修例，這樣才對市民公道。<br />\n<br />\n他又批評林鄭月娥拒絕辯論等於放棄聆聽意見的機會，證明她根本不打算向市民解釋修例及聆聽任何意見，不將香港市民放在眼內，又質疑林鄭月娥不敢接戰「是否害怕真理愈辯愈明」，擔心市民了解修例只會有更多人參與反修例遊行。"},{"pid":"ddf688687ad577335f9750fdc2d938cef0cca612","tid":1176363,"uid":176679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T10:07:31.000Z","msg":"佢不嬲都冇諗住解釋 佢講啲野都只係純粹包裝到件事好睇啲 你反對你嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72c3e6d5d060eed292d5fe2c7e2dd409eb1f8055","tid":1176363,"uid":168368,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T16:40:07.000Z","msg":"呢條濫權婆你唔賣起佢  佢只會推行更多惡法 話之你 佢睇死香港人冇槍權 港豬多  東亞病夫性格 又多既得利益者"},{"pid":"81e80c2644b268172bae540b50b3dc5a4a07c9ce","tid":1176363,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T16:41:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2fe3c5665fb77a36ad4309d8a5da93816cd26e0","tid":1176363,"uid":189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T16:42:30.000Z","msg":"宜家紳士都唔扮嚟呃吓啲廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9939cc8dd6031534e72347c5544dc688d6bc56b9","tid":1176363,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T00:52:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fa